title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sim Update VII - Photogrammetry Utrecht
description:
Asobo has released Sim Update VII today. As part of this update several photogrammetry cities have been added amongst them Utrecht. In this video we will fly over the city center and over other parts of the city to see how realistic the scenery is and what the quality of the scenery is.
